com.caseybrooks.androidbibletools.enumeration

Enum Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Version>
      • com.caseybrooks.androidbibletools.enumeration.Version
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Version>

    public enum Version
extends java.lang.Enum<Version>
    Enumerates several English translations of the Bible according to their name and the number of chapters in that book. Using the static method parseBook will attempt to find the appropriate enumeration given a string of the version's full name or its code.
